videos.description: Texas Tech's Davide Moretti throws a lob for Tariq Owens to rise up over the defense and dunk.
videos.headline: Owens makes difficult catch before alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Alex Robinson takes his defender off the dribble and finishes at the basket with a smooth reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (TCU's Robinson makes sweet reverse layup) 2019/3/2

videos.headline: TCU's Robinson makes sweet reverse layup

videos.description: Tariq Owens tries to top Jarret Culver's dunk in the open court but ends up blowing the dunk attempt.
videos.headline: Owens botches wide-open dunk attempt

videos.description: Davide Moretti draws the defense on the drive and sets Tariq Owens up for a powerful two-handed dunk in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Moretti sets Owens up for a powerful two-handed dunk) 2019/3/2

videos.headline: Moretti sets Owens up for a powerful two-handed dunk
